# 👨‍🏫 Mentor's Note

We're now thinking like product designers.

Many first-time developers start coding immediately and keep redesigning the app later. That often leads to wasted effort.

By defining the screens and user journey first, we'll have a clear blueprint. When we eventually build the Flutter app or generate code with AI, we'll already know exactly what each screen should contain and how users move through the app.

From Day 23 onward, we'll start turning these screen ideas into a complete technical blueprint that can guide development.
